Chloe Owens came up with the idea for Bump 2 Breast when she was pregnant with daughter Lola . 
  She had no idea what to expect and struggled to remember which breast to use when breastfeeding . 
  Chloe designed the app to guide mothers through pregnancy and early motherhood . 
  It has already been downloaded 20,000 times and helps breastfeeding mothers remember which boob to use . 
 